reviewtext: Exceeded the use for what  I needed .... Very good cord for the price .... The "5e" is for extra heavy duty wire gauge.Hooks up in a snap and doesn't come out of the plug unless you need it to...... The end plug is made with very good quality.... Thanks for sending it to me the way you did,  I received it one day before the promised date...
summary: CAT 5e .... Stands for Extra Heavy Gauge wire......  Not really needed  for this lentgh  of 7 feet.  But an extra feature
